'''''Ottran''''' ({{lang-en|A Spy}}) is a 2003 [[Tamil language|Tamil]] [[film]] starring [[Arjun Sarja]], [[Simran (actress)|Simran]], [[Manorama (actress)|Manorama]], [[Vadivelu]], [[Tejashree]], [[Sarath Babu]] and [[Film director|directed]] by Ilankannan. The [[Film score|score]] and [[soundtrack]] was composed by [[Pravin Mani]]. The film was a hit at [[box office]].<ref>{{cite news|last=Pillai|first=Sreedhar|url=http://www.hindu.com/mp/2003/12/29/stories/2003122900170100.htm|title= Reel of fortune |accessdate=2013-09-06|date=2003-12-29|newspaper=[[The Hindu]]|location=Chennai, India}}</ref>

